
1  

Ido koany, konyou etuŋanan loka Edeke ko Yuda kakirot naka EJAKAIT kobu Betel: abwoi Yeroboam eiduny ketem aisupuruun lukisupuru. 
2  

Kilamak etem kakirot naka EJAKAIT, kotema atiar, “Wu etem, etem, inera kwanata EJAKAIT ebe, ‘Koany, ewuruunio ikoku kokek loka Daudi, ekekiror Yosia; einakini ŋesi kamakon isasedotin luka aiboisio nuiceleleete luisupuruunete lukisupurununo kamakon araun asuban, icweikinete kesi akojo nuka ituŋa kamakon.’ ” 
3  

Koinak aanyunet kapaaran kaŋin, ebe, “Na ŋes aanyunet naenera EJAKAIT: koany, ecila etem, ebukor ekurwon loejai tomake.” 
4  

Kosodi kanen, kepupu ekabaka akirot naka etuŋanan loka Edeke, naelamia ŋesi etem koBetel, kikia Yeroboam akekan kotem, kotema ebe, “Kikam ŋes.” Koono akekan naekiarit adoditor ŋes, komam epedori asukokin. 
5  Kocila etem da, kobukor ekurwon kotem, kwape ajaar aanyunet naabu etuŋanan loka Edeke koinak kakirot naka EJAKAIT. 
6  

Koboŋok ekabaka kotema etuŋanan loka Edeke ebe, “Kiŋaiŋa cabo asianut naka EJAKAIT Ekonideke, kilipakinai eoŋ, koŋaleu akakan.” Kiŋaiŋa etuŋanan loka Edeke EJAKAIT, kitaŋaleunai akekan, kojaun kwape lem sek. 
7  

Kotema ekabaka etuŋanan loka Edeke atiar, “Kaloto ore, kikwaru, kainakini jo ainakinet.” 
8  

Kotema etuŋanan loka Edeke ekabaka atiar, “Arai kiinaki ijo eoŋ atutubet naka etogokon, mam eoŋ alosi kajo, idomam anyami atap karaida aimat akipi kaibois kana. 
9  

Naarai aponi kecorakinitete eoŋ kakirot naka EJAKAIT ebe, ‘Mam inyami atap, karaida aimat akipi, karaida aboŋor korot lokibunio.’ ” 
10  Kosodi koboŋo kecerot, mam abu koboŋo korot kaloabunio Betel.


11  Kiboienenei enabi lomojoŋ koBetel; kobu ediopet kodweke kolimok ŋes aswamisio kere nueswama etuŋanan loka Edeke kapaaran kaŋin koBetel: akiro nuabu ŋesi kolimok ekabaka, ŋun da kolimokis papakec. 
12  Kotema papakec kes ebe, “Etoro bo ŋesi orot ali?” Apotu odweke koanyut erot loetori etuŋanan loka Edeke, loabunit koYuda. 
13  Kotema odweke atiar, “Kopesikinai lupetan asigiria.” Kosodete kesi apesikin lupetan asigiria: kibwanen ŋesi. 
14  Kibwapak etuŋanan loka Edeke, kodum ŋes iboie kotolim kelua: kotema ŋes atiar, “Ijo ŋes etuŋanan loka Edeke loabuni koYuda?” Kotema atiar, “Eoŋ lo,” 
15  Kosodi atemar ŋes atiar, “Kaboŋosi oreka, konyam atap.” 
16  Kotema atiar, “Mam apedori aboŋor kajo, karaida alomar kajo: mam da anyami atap karaida aimat akipi kajo kaibois kana: 
17  

Naarai aponi kalimokinitete kakirot naka EJAKAIT ebe, ‘Sirikinyam atap, karaida aimat akipi kaŋina, sirikiboŋo da korot loibu kobunio.’ ” 
18  

Kotema ŋes atiar, “Eoŋ da enabi kwape kajo; abu emalaika kalimok eoŋ kakirot naka EJAKAIT ebe, ‘Kinyaku ŋes togokon, konyam atap, komat akipi.’ ” Konye abu kiŋalai. 
19  Kwaŋin koboŋo kaŋes, konyam atap kotogoke, komat akipi.


20  

Kosodi kanen enyamete, kobu akirot naka EJAKAIT mama ejai enabi loabu kinyaku ŋes: 
21  Kiworo mama ejai etuŋanan loka Edeke loabunit koYuda ebe, “Inera EJAKAIT kwanata ebe, ‘Naarai ipaliiki ijo akirot naka EJAKAIT, mam iricit aicorakinet naecoraki EJAKAIT Ekonideke jo. 
22  Konye iboŋu, inyama atap, imat akipi kaibois nakilimokinio jo ebe, “Sirikinyam atap, sirikimat akipi”; mam akuanakon idaikinio ates naka lukapapaakon.’ ” 
23  Kosodi kanen kedau ŋesi ainyam atap, ka aimat, kopesik lupetan asigiria enabi loenyakuni ŋesi. 
24  

Napelosi, kiriamakinos keŋatuny korot, koar eŋatuny ŋes, kocakak akekuan orot, kobwo asigiria die kaŋes; kobwo da eŋatuny die kakekuan. 
25  Ido koany, kitoroto ituŋa, koanyutu akuan korot, eŋatuny da ebwoi die kates; kopotu, koyaut akiro ore neeboieneno enabi ŋol lomojoŋ.


26  Kepupu ŋun enabi loabu kinyaku ŋes korot, kotema atiar, “Ŋes ŋol etuŋanan loka Edeke, loabu kipaliik akirot naka EJAKAIT: kanuka ŋun ejaiki EJAKAIT ŋes mama ejai eŋatuny, loapoopoo ŋes, aara da, kwape ajaar akirot naka EJAKAIT, naabu kiner kaŋes.” 
27  Kolimok odweke ebe, “Kopesikinai lupetan asigiria.” Kopesikis. 
28  

Kolot, kodum aketes korot, ka asigiria ka eŋatuny ebwoete die kates: mam abu eŋatuny konyamite ates, karaida apoopo asigiria. 
29  Kodaku enabi ates naka etuŋanan loka Edeke, kidokok asigiria, kinyaku ore, aibworo ka ainuk ŋes. 
30  

Kibwaik akuanake atesike elopet; kibworoto ŋes ebe, “Wu okwe onaceka!” 
31  

Kosodi kanen, kedau ainuk ŋes kotema odweke ebe, “Katwana eoŋ, konukakis eoŋ ates neenukuk etuŋanan loka Edeke; kibwaikis akakojo eiduny kakekojo. 
32  

Naarai abeit itodolikinio akirot naabu ŋesi kiworo kakirot naka EJAKAIT ilamakini etem koBet-el, ilamakini da itogoi kere luka aiboisio nuiceleleete nuejaas oreria luka Samaria.”


33  

Akaulo kaŋun mam abu Yeroboam koboŋu korotoke loerono, konye kiyatak aseun kotuŋa kere lukitarauni isasedotin luka aiboisio nuiceleleete: ŋol kere loekoto, kotiakuni, tetere ejaas isasedotin luka aiboisio nuiceleleete. 
34  

Koraun akirot ŋin adiakaret kokek loka Yeroboam, agelar ŋes, ka amudiar ŋes kakwap.

